1. *Pođi* odavde! (Go away from here!)
2. *Pođimo* večeras u klub. (Let's go to the club tonight.)
3. On je tražio da *pođe* sa nama. (He asked to go with us.)
4. Ona je očekivala da će *poći* na more. (She was expecting to go to the sea.)
5. *Pošao* je bez ikakvog objašnjenja. (He left without any explanation.)
6. Čekamo da *pođu* naši prijatelji. (We are waiting for our friends to come.)